API (Application Programming Interface)


Presentation Layer
Business Layer (API works with Business Payer)
Database Layer

API works on HTTP protocol.
HTTP Methods:

->  GET (Get existing information from data base)
->  POST (Create new entry)
->  PUT (Create new entry as well and update existing entry)
->  PATCH  (Update specific field  of information)
->  DELETE (Delete data from database)

Response status code:
100 - 199 : (Information status code)
200 - 299 : (Success operations)
300 - 399 : (Re-directional error)
400 - 499 :  (Client Error)
500 - 599 :  (Server Error)
